1
00:00:04,050 --> 00:00:06,999
♫ <i> Nowhere to escape </i> ♫

2
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:09,959
♫ <i> No one to rely on </i> ♫

3
00:00:09,960 --> 00:00:14,030
♫ <i> Withdrawing smiles </i> ♫

4
00:00:15,860 --> 00:00:18,869
♫ <i> Never give in </i> ♫

5
00:00:18,870 --> 00:00:24,050
♫ <i> Forget about one's youth </i> ♫

6
00:00:25,850 --> 00:00:28,820
♫ <i> I've never been afraid of loneliness when
embarking on this journey </i> ♫

7
00:00:28,820 --> 00:00:31,690
♫ <i> Tears and regrets go hand in hand </i> ♫

8
00:00:31,690 --> 00:00:34,590
♫ <i>But my heart is still fiery-hot</i> ♫

9
00:00:34,590 --> 00:00:37,740
♫ <i>To the distance</i> ♫

10
00:00:37,740 --> 00:00:40,610
♫ <i>The miserable past is like a dagger</i> ♫

11
00:00:40,610 --> 00:00:43,620
♫ <i>Though my wings are broken</i> ♫

12
00:00:43,620 --> 00:00:50,340
♫ <i>I will keep flying</i> ♫

13
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:56,199
♫ <i>Following the direction of the light</i> ♫

14
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:58,359
♫ <i>I'll forget you</i> ♫

15
00:00:58,360 --> 00:01:04,359
♫ <i>The memory shaped my stubbornness</i> ♫

16
00:01:04,359 --> 00:01:07,359
♫ <i>By virtue of the light in the dark night</i> ♫

17
00:01:07,360 --> 00:01:10,309
♫ <i>I'll return it with a long ballad</i> ♫

18
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:12,369
♫ <i>The river of life is under my feet</i> ♫

19
00:01:12,369 --> 00:01:16,960
♫ <i>I don't regret my craziness</i> ♫

20
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:32,819
<i>[The Long Ballad]</i>

21
00:01:32,820 --> 00:01:36,200
<i>[Episode 30]</i>

22
00:01:44,340 --> 00:01:51,460
<i>[Non-Interference]</i>

23
00:01:58,630 --> 00:02:01,839
Let me see. Which brat dares to crash into Liuyun Taoist Temple?

24
00:02:01,839 --> 00:02:04,479
Boy. Come out!

25
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:14,619
For a hundred years, you are the first one

26
00:02:14,619 --> 00:02:16,399
who has broken into the Liuyun Taoist Temple without permission.

27
00:02:16,399 --> 00:02:18,079
Don't you think it is not good for a man

28
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:21,938
to break into a temple full of nuns?

29
00:02:21,939 --> 00:02:25,339
Sorry, I just want to look for an old friend.

30
00:02:25,340 --> 00:02:29,919
I told you that nobody here is called Li Changge or Li Shisi.

31
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,339
<i>My name is Li Changge.</i>

32
00:02:33,340 --> 00:02:35,800
<i>Master Situ, thank you for teaching me the swordsmanship.</i>

33
00:02:39,420 --> 00:02:41,179
You're too arrogant.

34
00:02:41,180 --> 00:02:43,339
Come and leave as you like?

35
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:47,498
I told you that I didn't mean to provoke you here.

36
00:02:47,499 --> 00:02:49,539
I'm just looking for someone.

37
00:02:51,100 --> 00:02:52,938
Do you want to fight with me?

38
00:02:52,939 --> 00:02:54,500
Do you think you can win?

39
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:55,578
You can have a try.

40
00:02:55,579 --> 00:02:56,880
Both of you should stop.

41
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:58,459
The temple is a quiet and peaceful place.

42
00:02:58,460 --> 00:03:00,298
Don't disturb the rest of the Taoists.

43
00:03:00,299 --> 00:03:02,738
Mister Situ, don't irritate him.

44
00:03:02,739 --> 00:03:05,160
Let him get out of here quickly.

45
00:03:07,939 --> 00:03:09,559
Boring.

46
00:03:09,559 --> 00:03:11,259
My apologies.

47
00:03:11,260 --> 00:03:13,378
I want to find my friend so much.

48
00:03:13,379 --> 00:03:15,360
I'm so eager that...

49
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:18,678
I've already told you that Taoist Sun saved countless girls.

50
00:03:18,678 --> 00:03:20,759
You'd better leave soon.

51
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:22,960
Excuse me.

52
00:03:24,980 --> 00:03:28,960
<i>[Sun]</i>

53
00:03:38,370 --> 00:03:41,960
Does my apprentice Li Changge have another name called Li Shisi?

54
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:44,729
Doesn't she feel troubled to have so many names?

55
00:03:44,730 --> 00:03:48,760
But things get more interesting when she meets her friend.

56
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:09,900
<i>[Liuyun Taoist Temple]</i>

57
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:21,800
Li Changge,

58
00:04:24,659 --> 00:04:26,559
where are you?

59
00:04:35,499 --> 00:04:37,299
Let's take a break and drink a cup of tea.

60
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:38,800
Okay.

61
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,739
- Ladies, what do you want to drink?
- Tea, thank you.

62
00:04:47,739 --> 00:04:49,580
Okay, please wait a minute.

63
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:53,639
It's said that there will be a heavy fire in Luoyang within three days.

64
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:55,079
The drought has been serious recently.

65
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:57,458
We don't have even enough water to drink. If it is true,

66
00:04:57,459 --> 00:04:59,160
where should we get the water to put out the fire?

67
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:01,160
What should we do?

68
00:05:01,160 --> 00:05:02,720
What are you worrying about?

69
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:07,400
I've heard that the fire won't be here.

70
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:09,840
Why?

71
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:12,218
Liu, do you have a secret?

72
00:05:12,219 --> 00:05:13,739
Say it.

73
00:05:13,740 --> 00:05:17,119
Luoyang suffers from both drought and fire.

74
00:05:17,119 --> 00:05:19,020
Just wait.

75
00:05:19,020 --> 00:05:22,500
Heaven will let us know

76
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:27,040
who has brought disaster to Luoyang in two days.

77
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:31,300
A'Li?

78
00:05:32,270 --> 00:05:33,670
Enjoy the tea.

79
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:37,460
Look at you! What are you thinking about?

80
00:05:37,460 --> 00:05:39,360
The tea is not ready.

81
00:05:41,710 --> 00:05:43,178
Enjoy your tea.

82
00:05:43,178 --> 00:05:44,979
Bye.

83
00:05:44,980 --> 00:05:46,320
You didn't finish your talk!

84
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:49,100
- You just talk about half of it.
- I'm going to buy something.

85
00:05:52,299 --> 00:05:53,658
<i>Sachets on sale!</i>

86
00:05:53,659 --> 00:05:55,600
<i>Have a look!</i>

87
00:06:35,780 --> 00:06:37,899
Where did you go?

88
00:06:37,899 --> 00:06:40,058
Why are you so improper and impolite?

89
00:06:40,059 --> 00:06:42,139
At least we are taking action together now.

90
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:45,420
But you ignore our Yanxing Sect's rules.

91
00:06:49,899 --> 00:06:51,879
Tell us. What's wrong?

92
00:06:51,879 --> 00:06:54,600
I went to Liuyun Taoist Temple that harbors refugees.

93
00:06:55,740 --> 00:06:58,369
Sun Simiao has saved too many girls.

94
00:06:58,370 --> 00:07:00,670
It's like looking for a needle in a haystack.

95
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:04,139
I even went in to search in person.

96
00:07:04,140 --> 00:07:06,840
If she's there, she won't refuse to come out.

97
00:07:11,260 --> 00:07:12,720
I was wrong.

98
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,939
You didn't finish.

99
00:07:13,939 --> 00:07:15,699
Come on.

100
00:07:15,699 --> 00:07:17,520
Don't be anxious.

101
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:20,559
We can definitely find our young master.

102
00:07:22,119 --> 00:07:25,879
Xu Feng was right just now.

103
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:29,799
We'd better inform each other before taking any action

104
00:07:29,799 --> 00:07:31,819
in case of any trouble.

105
00:07:31,820 --> 00:07:35,239
Besides, Young Master Qin's identity is special.

106
00:07:35,239 --> 00:07:38,119
You should be more careful before taking any action.

107
00:07:38,119 --> 00:07:44,079
As far as I think, you should let us search for the young master.

108
00:07:59,330 --> 00:08:00,790
Finally, you're back.

109
00:08:00,799 --> 00:08:03,218
You know what? Shortly after your leaving,

110
00:08:03,219 --> 00:08:06,859
a gentleman rushed in and said he was looking for someone.

111
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:07,859
He kept messing up.

112
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:10,110
It is Mister Situ that drove him away finally.

113
00:08:10,110 --> 00:08:11,519
What?

114
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:14,480
If I were here, I'd scold him bitterly.

115
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:18,240
How can we allow him to do that in Liuyun Taoist Temple?

116
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:21,480
By the way, A'Li, he's been to your room.

117
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,519
Go and check if you have lost anything.

118
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:26,318
It's okay. I have nothing important.

119
00:08:26,318 --> 00:08:30,279
<i>Luoyang suffers from both drought and fire. Just wait.</i>

120
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:33,579
<i>Heaven will let us know</i>

121
00:08:33,579 --> 00:08:37,499
<i>who has brought disasters to Luoyang in two days.</i>

122
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:40,099
<i>The rumor about the fire in Luoyang is not that simple.</i>

123
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:43,239
<i>Who did that man want to indicate?</i>

124
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,420
Prince and Princess, do you know

125
00:08:48,420 --> 00:08:50,640
that the rumor about Luoyang is spreading out?

126
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:54,980
It is said that Luoyang must catch fire within three days.

127
00:08:57,019 --> 00:08:59,100
Princess Yongan, your appearance shows

128
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:00,679
that you must have known it before.

129
00:09:00,679 --> 00:09:05,599
But Hao Du heard another rumor in the liquor shop today.

130
00:09:05,599 --> 00:09:07,960
They said the crown prince never showed up

131
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:11,200
because he's addicted to having fun.

132
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:13,880
What's more, the candles are always lit in the Ziwei Palace,

133
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:17,500
which seems to be the hidden danger of the fire.

134
00:09:22,799 --> 00:09:24,840
Sister, I didn't.

135
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:26,880
It's not true.

136
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:29,759
Who spread this nonsense first?

137
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:31,660
Hao Du, where did you hear this?

138
00:09:31,660 --> 00:09:35,100
Capture all these villains who spread rumors to deceive the people.

139
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:38,220
The rumors usually come from whorehouses.

140
00:09:38,220 --> 00:09:41,479
But now it is discussed even in the normal shops of liquor.

141
00:09:41,479 --> 00:09:45,259
It seems hard to stop it now.

142
00:09:48,640 --> 00:09:50,419
What to do then?

143
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:52,600
Put out the candles and pick up an auspicious day.

144
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:56,620
Dress in formal clothes with the crown to pray for happiness to Heaven.

145
00:09:56,620 --> 00:09:59,579
Your Highness, you also should visit the refugees' shelters in person,

146
00:09:59,579 --> 00:10:01,960
wearing plain clothes without golden belts.

147
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:05,940
Therefore, Your Highness's sincerity can be seen.

148
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,000
<i>[Qianyang Hall]</i>

149
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:23,479
<i>Minister Du, please wait.</i>

150
00:10:26,300 --> 00:10:27,699
Minister Du,

151
00:10:27,699 --> 00:10:30,880
the rumor just said that there would be a heavy fire in Luoyang.

152
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:34,059
But I think someone must bring this gossip

153
00:10:34,059 --> 00:10:36,479
and the crown prince together on purpose.

154
00:10:36,479 --> 00:10:40,939
Your Highness, I see you in a totally new light after a few days.

155
00:10:40,940 --> 00:10:43,138
What you said is absolutely right.

156
00:10:43,139 --> 00:10:44,640
But, Your Highness, please be assured,

157
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:47,400
I will definitely deal with it properly.

158
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:49,699
Good job, Minister Du.

159
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:59,380
<i>[Qianyang Hall]</i>

160
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:19,430
Chunfeng,

161
00:11:19,430 --> 00:11:24,660
have you leaked the news about the abnormal astronomical phenomena to others?

162
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:29,000
Your Majesty, the armillary sphere shows

163
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:32,338
that there might be a disaster of fire in Luoyang within three days

164
00:11:32,339 --> 00:11:34,119
and the crown prince is in Luoyang.

165
00:11:34,119 --> 00:11:38,860
I just told these facts to Minister Du objectively.

166
00:11:38,860 --> 00:11:43,659
I asked him to take good care of His Highness.

167
00:11:43,659 --> 00:11:45,619
Look at my unfilial son.

168
00:11:45,619 --> 00:11:48,059
I'll punish him when he's back.

169
00:11:48,060 --> 00:11:51,099
Do you know what Du said in the letter?

170
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:53,458
I let him investigate the situation of the disaster in Luoyang

171
00:11:53,459 --> 00:11:57,640
while he kept having fun in the Ziwei Palace.

172
00:11:57,640 --> 00:12:00,100
None of his action is like a crown prince.

173
00:12:00,100 --> 00:12:06,419
But to my delight, Du told me that Yan kept helping this brat

174
00:12:06,420 --> 00:12:10,778
resettle the refugees in Luoyang.

175
00:12:10,779 --> 00:12:14,900
She's got the spirit of a princess of our great Tang.

176
00:12:15,559 --> 00:12:19,519
I realize Yan'er has grown up by her change.

177
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:25,039
But the price of growing up is always suffering.

178
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:28,338
This daughter of mine...

179
00:12:28,339 --> 00:12:34,679
makes me take pity on her but feel happy at the same time.

180
00:12:34,679 --> 00:12:37,780
Her Highness considers the sorrow of the people,

181
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:40,080
which is the bliss of Great Tang.

182
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:42,459
The crown prince is still young.

183
00:12:42,459 --> 00:12:44,360
I believe he can share the burden and problems

184
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:47,619
for Your Majesty after abundant experiences.

185
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:49,918
Chunfeng, you don't need to speak for him,

186
00:12:49,918 --> 00:12:52,569
he should learn his lessons.

187
00:12:52,570 --> 00:12:55,440
He might be soberer in this way.

188
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,640
Your Majesty.

189
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:16,459
This is Hexagram Shi, which means success after danger.

190
00:13:16,459 --> 00:13:20,939
The story in Luoyang might be very interesting.

191
00:13:36,559 --> 00:13:38,579
<i>Hold on.</i>

192
00:13:40,819 --> 00:13:42,719
<i>Have patience.</i>

193
00:13:42,719 --> 00:13:45,498
It's not serious.

194
00:13:45,498 --> 00:13:47,138
The muscles and bones are not injured.

195
00:13:47,139 --> 00:13:52,479
But do not get in touch with filthy water when you're back.

196
00:13:52,479 --> 00:13:53,619
Understood?

197
00:13:53,620 --> 00:13:55,279
Okay? Bind up over there.

198
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:56,800
Thank you.

199
00:14:06,679 --> 00:14:08,379
Do not get in touch with the water these days.

200
00:14:08,379 --> 00:14:09,979
Okay.

201
00:14:25,239 --> 00:14:27,159
Why are you here?

202
00:14:27,159 --> 00:14:29,059
I'm worried about you.

203
00:14:29,059 --> 00:14:32,300
Just in case, you'd better hide outside the city.

204
00:14:32,300 --> 00:14:35,299
Both Minister Du and Hao Du are in Luoyang now.

205
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:36,340
What if...

206
00:14:36,340 --> 00:14:38,160
I'm done. You can get your medicine.

207
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,540
Thank you.

208
00:14:39,540 --> 00:14:41,140
<i>Thanks.</i>

209
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:49,340
Didn't you say that His Majesty would not kill me?

210
00:14:49,340 --> 00:14:52,200
His Majesty's favor is grand so he didn't mind it long before.

211
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:55,400
But you're afraid that Du Ruhui will disobey the order.

212
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:07,400
Wei Shuyu, why are you still vacillating?

213
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:09,559
After enduring great danger several times,

214
00:15:09,559 --> 00:15:11,200
I'm not fearful of these anymore.

215
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:13,359
I'm not faltering.

216
00:15:13,359 --> 00:15:16,620
I dare not to make you take risks anymore.

217
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:18,139
You don't fear death.

218
00:15:18,139 --> 00:15:20,459
But I'm afraid of your death.

219
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:27,960
These days are the peak season of the Liuyun Taoist Temple.

220
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:31,640
I won't be able to leave nor do I want to leave.

221
00:15:32,619 --> 00:15:33,640
Let me help you.

222
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:35,340
Thank you.

223
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:04,770
<i>[Honestly is the best way]</i>

224
00:16:04,770 --> 00:16:06,458
Father, you never believe in God or Buddha,

225
00:16:06,459 --> 00:16:08,459
why do you come to this temple today?

226
00:16:08,459 --> 00:16:10,358
It's not I don't believe.

227
00:16:10,358 --> 00:16:13,540
I'm just not persistent or superstitious.

228
00:16:13,540 --> 00:16:16,039
One day before we set off from Chang'an,

229
00:16:16,039 --> 00:16:20,039
Li Chunfeng gave me a bag with a tip.

230
00:16:20,039 --> 00:16:24,159
It's written that I have to come here when I arrive in Luoyang.

231
00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:30,059
<i>Hurry.</i>

232
00:16:30,060 --> 00:16:33,439
<i>I see your head is dim while the feet are cold.</i>

233
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:35,458
<i>It seems that you can't live longer than a year.</i>

234
00:16:35,459 --> 00:16:38,559
<i>You are dying within this period.</i>

235
00:16:39,359 --> 00:16:41,260
<i>I know it clearly.</i>

236
00:16:41,260 --> 00:16:43,159
<i>I observed your fortune just now.</i>

237
00:16:43,160 --> 00:16:45,018
<i>The result is positive.</i>

238
00:16:45,019 --> 00:16:46,400
<i>Take this tip.</i>

239
00:16:46,400 --> 00:16:48,080
<i>Open it after you arrive in Luoyang.</i>

240
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:51,080
<i>Go there on the seventh day of the lunar calendar.</i>

241
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:54,880
<i>Probably, you will encounter some chances there.</i>

242
00:16:57,840 --> 00:17:00,960
This fortune teller always indicates something behind his words.

243
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:05,700
Now that we're in Luoyang, why not come and have a look?

244
00:17:21,780 --> 00:17:24,780
Gentlemen, it seems that you aren't visiting Taoist Sun for your disease.

245
00:17:24,780 --> 00:17:26,520
May I know what your purpose is?

246
00:17:26,520 --> 00:17:32,359
Is Taoist Sun called Sun Simiao?

247
00:17:32,360 --> 00:17:34,978
Sure. Can anyone else called Taoist Sun

248
00:17:34,978 --> 00:17:37,599
treat so many patients for free in this world?

249
00:17:37,599 --> 00:17:39,139
Assistant Minister Li asked you to come here

250
00:17:39,140 --> 00:17:41,959
so that Taoist Sun can treat your disease.

251
00:17:42,560 --> 00:17:44,560
Taoist lady, please help to report

252
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:47,959
that Minister of War, Du Ruhui, wants to see Taoist Sun.

253
00:17:47,959 --> 00:17:49,479
How can you see him as you like?

254
00:17:49,479 --> 00:17:51,239
How do I know if you are telling the truth?

255
00:17:51,239 --> 00:17:53,240
Someone just messed up in Liuyun Taoist Temple yesterday.

256
00:17:53,240 --> 00:17:55,960
All kinds of people can be here now, right?

257
00:17:58,040 --> 00:18:00,140
Look at this clearly.

258
00:18:00,140 --> 00:18:02,599
Anyway, I don't know what this is.

259
00:18:02,599 --> 00:18:05,719
But no matter if you are the Minister of War or World,

260
00:18:05,719 --> 00:18:08,260
the sole rule of Liuyun Taoist Temple is first-come, first-served.

261
00:18:08,260 --> 00:18:11,490
Please follow the rule and wait in line.

262
00:18:23,540 --> 00:18:26,280
Changge, it is about your safety.

263
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:28,619
We can't take it randomly.

264
00:18:28,619 --> 00:18:31,219
A'Li.

265
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:35,200
Yes?

266
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:38,980
Go and get ten cicada sloughs from the pharmacy outside now.

267
00:18:38,980 --> 00:18:41,520
Okay, wait for me for a few minutes.

268
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:45,260
Taoist Sun, there are two people in decent clothes outside,

269
00:18:45,260 --> 00:18:46,880
called the ministers of something.

270
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,540
They are asking to see you.

271
00:18:48,540 --> 00:18:50,079
Ministry of what? War? World?

272
00:18:50,079 --> 00:18:51,719
Forget it, let them wait outside in line.

273
00:18:51,719 --> 00:18:53,319
Okay.

274
00:18:58,859 --> 00:19:00,259
Gentlemen, please wait in line.

275
00:19:00,259 --> 00:19:01,959
Thank you.

276
00:19:13,439 --> 00:19:15,139
Wei Shuyu, what...

277
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:24,599
What are you looking at?

278
00:19:24,599 --> 00:19:28,619
Father, I think I've seen an old friend.

279
00:19:29,560 --> 00:19:30,640
I'll be back soon.

280
00:19:30,640 --> 00:19:32,040
Okay.

281
00:19:45,479 --> 00:19:49,619
Sir, are you interested in the pharmacy of our Taoist temple?

282
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:56,000
I'm sorry.

283
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:58,880
I just saw someone sneak into the pharmacy.

284
00:19:58,880 --> 00:20:00,479
Sneak?

285
00:20:00,479 --> 00:20:02,580
Liuyun Taoist Temple is an open and upright place,

286
00:20:02,580 --> 00:20:04,100
<i>we save people and benefit society.</i>

287
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:06,460
<i>How could there be any sneaky person here?</i>

288
00:20:06,460 --> 00:20:08,060
<i>You must be Minister Du.</i>

289
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:09,540
Hello, Taoist.

290
00:20:09,540 --> 00:20:12,379
This young gentleman entered Liuyun Taoist Temple

291
00:20:12,379 --> 00:20:14,359
and went straight towards my pharmacy.

292
00:20:14,359 --> 00:20:17,880
May I know if there is anything wrong with my pharmacy?

293
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:20,660
Nowadays, the refugees are everywhere in Luoyang, mixed up with nice and evil people.

294
00:20:20,660 --> 00:20:24,119
Hao Du is afraid that some hostile people are taking a chance to carry on misdeeds.

295
00:20:24,119 --> 00:20:26,818
That would disturb you and the Taoist priests.

296
00:20:26,819 --> 00:20:28,178
Thanks for being concerned.

297
00:20:28,179 --> 00:20:31,259
However, Liuyun Taoist Temple is pure and poor as water.

298
00:20:31,260 --> 00:20:33,239
It's unnecessary for gangsters to consider us.

299
00:20:33,239 --> 00:20:37,019
You might have seen it wrong.

300
00:20:39,819 --> 00:20:41,119
Please.

301
00:20:55,239 --> 00:20:57,880
Why is Du Ruhui here?

302
00:20:57,880 --> 00:21:00,079
Changge, it is too dangerous here.

303
00:21:00,079 --> 00:21:02,079
You'd better leave with me.

304
00:21:02,079 --> 00:21:03,920
Leave with you?

305
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:05,599
And then?

306
00:21:05,599 --> 00:21:07,920
I'll manage ways to protect you.

307
00:21:07,920 --> 00:21:11,058
Changge, I really want to keep you safe.

308
00:21:11,059 --> 00:21:15,200
Can you trust me for the last time?

309
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:17,280
I don't distrust you.

310
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:22,578
But if I had any other idea, I wouldn't stay here now.

311
00:21:22,579 --> 00:21:27,080
What's more, I haven't got the answer I want.

312
00:21:27,080 --> 00:21:29,060
What's that?

313
00:21:29,839 --> 00:21:34,379
Shuyu, I believe that you must have your own business in Luoyang Office.

314
00:21:34,379 --> 00:21:35,599
Just go.

315
00:21:35,599 --> 00:21:38,420
I don't really fear them.

316
00:21:38,420 --> 00:21:40,199
I just have no time to deal with them.

317
00:21:40,199 --> 00:21:42,058
So I'll manage to avoid them.

318
00:21:42,059 --> 00:21:43,359
Just be assured.

319
00:21:43,359 --> 00:21:46,839
Changge. Changge!

320
00:22:08,419 --> 00:22:14,760
Since you were introduced by Chunfeng, I'll be straightforward.

321
00:22:15,800 --> 00:22:19,799
Minister Du, the rest of your life is limited.

322
00:22:22,000 --> 00:22:24,719
If you want to extend your life,

323
00:22:24,719 --> 00:22:30,099
the only way is to retire at the peak of your career.

324
00:22:30,100 --> 00:22:34,159
But as far as I can see,

325
00:22:34,159 --> 00:22:39,739
you're reluctant to give up your current business.

326
00:22:39,760 --> 00:22:44,480
At present, I can't,

327
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:47,839
dare not, and also don't want to give up.

328
00:22:47,839 --> 00:22:54,379
If you have got no way to cure my disease, let's just forget it.

329
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:57,520
If you're so worried about it.

330
00:22:58,380 --> 00:23:01,360
I can just extend your life

331
00:23:01,360 --> 00:23:05,590
for three years within my power.

332
00:23:05,599 --> 00:23:08,238
But, after this,

333
00:23:08,238 --> 00:23:11,830
you may be quite miserable

334
00:23:11,830 --> 00:23:15,400
when you meet your death in the future.

335
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:19,358
Three years are enough for me.

336
00:23:19,358 --> 00:23:21,469
Taoist priest, please help me.

337
00:23:21,469 --> 00:23:22,978
Are you sure it is worth it?

338
00:23:22,978 --> 00:23:26,779
Taoist priests, when you two help the poor and miserable in Liuyun Taoist Temple,

339
00:23:26,779 --> 00:23:30,130
have you ever thought about where poverty and sorrow come from?

340
00:23:30,130 --> 00:23:33,289
Heaven and Earth are ruthless while everything has its fate.

341
00:23:33,290 --> 00:23:35,300
These are their doomed disaster.

342
00:23:35,300 --> 00:23:37,580
Taoist priest, you are the hermit,

343
00:23:37,580 --> 00:23:41,419
but there are millions of people bothered by human society.

344
00:23:41,420 --> 00:23:45,338
<i>They have nowhere to hide and can only struggle for survival.</i>

345
00:23:45,339 --> 00:23:48,538
I read many books and work for the emperor.

346
00:23:48,539 --> 00:23:51,319
So I don't want to watch it without doing anything.

347
00:23:51,319 --> 00:23:53,880
His Majesty aims to build a prosperous society,

348
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:58,760
how can I make His Majesty go alone on this road?

349
00:23:58,760 --> 00:24:01,699
Three years are enough.

350
00:24:01,699 --> 00:24:05,559
I'm willing to spare no effort to assist His Majesty.

351
00:24:05,559 --> 00:24:10,580
Let's see if we can create a peaceful and prosperous era.

352
00:24:23,400 --> 00:24:26,218
Sister, what are they doing?

353
00:24:26,218 --> 00:24:28,899
Minister Du has said that tomorrow is the right time.

354
00:24:28,899 --> 00:24:32,300
Your Highness should take people to pray in White Horse Temple.

355
00:24:33,339 --> 00:24:34,799
Tomorrow?

356
00:24:34,799 --> 00:24:36,398
What's wrong?

357
00:24:36,398 --> 00:24:38,879
Nothing.

358
00:24:38,879 --> 00:24:44,318
Brother, from now on, you can't be childlike anymore.

359
00:24:44,318 --> 00:24:46,519
Our father is the emperor of the country now.

360
00:24:46,519 --> 00:24:49,338
So you can't be a good-for-nothing idler.

361
00:24:49,338 --> 00:24:51,459
- From today...
- Sister.

362
00:24:51,459 --> 00:24:53,680
What's wrong with you?

363
00:24:54,420 --> 00:24:57,299
After you got lost last time, you have become verbose now.

364
00:24:57,299 --> 00:24:58,999
You loved me the best.

365
00:24:59,000 --> 00:25:02,219
But why do you stand for the people like Minister Du?

366
00:25:02,219 --> 00:25:04,358
No matter how reluctant you are,

367
00:25:04,358 --> 00:25:07,958
you must follow the principle and show up tomorrow.

368
00:25:07,958 --> 00:25:10,199
I will play with you when it is finished.

369
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,578
Taoist Priest, thank you for helping me.

370
00:25:21,579 --> 00:25:25,099
I knew you went out to stop Minister Du on purpose.

371
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:28,879
But I didn't get...

372
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:33,520
It's a pity for you two to fight against each other.

373
00:25:34,020 --> 00:25:37,318
You know who I am?

374
00:25:37,318 --> 00:25:41,839
If you are not willing to say it, I won't ask more.

375
00:25:41,839 --> 00:25:47,039
But do you know what Minister Du's Dao is?

376
00:25:49,119 --> 00:25:52,139
He's not afraid of burning the candle at both ends,

377
00:25:52,140 --> 00:25:55,999
but he's worried that he can't see the prosperous Great Tang.

378
00:25:55,999 --> 00:25:58,559
<i>His Majesty aims to build a prosperous society,</i>

379
00:25:58,559 --> 00:26:03,418
<i>how can I make His Majesty go alone on this road?</i>

380
00:26:03,419 --> 00:26:05,218
<i>Three years are enough.</i>

381
00:26:05,219 --> 00:26:09,058
<i>I'm willing to spare no effort to assist His Majesty.</i>

382
00:26:09,058 --> 00:26:13,779
<i>Let's see if we can create a peaceful and prosperous era.</i>

383
00:26:13,780 --> 00:26:16,890
Maybe you two have got a similar Dao,

384
00:26:16,890 --> 00:26:21,330
but different strategies.

385
00:26:21,330 --> 00:26:24,438
Do you know what my Dao is?

386
00:26:24,438 --> 00:26:26,919
I can't say I know it.

387
00:26:26,919 --> 00:26:30,569
However, I think your intention is about governing,

388
00:26:30,570 --> 00:26:35,900
but I heard the method you selected tends to wreak havoc.

389
00:26:36,579 --> 00:26:41,499
What if I disobey the instruction and take my own way?

390
00:26:41,499 --> 00:26:43,899
For a river,

391
00:26:43,900 --> 00:26:47,938
roes, deer, tigers, or wolves drinking the water makes no difference.

392
00:26:47,939 --> 00:26:50,099
What's more, the tigers and wolves have their own Dao.

393
00:26:50,100 --> 00:26:53,358
The ones who should terminate them are the hunters.

394
00:26:53,358 --> 00:26:56,019
What are they to the river?

395
00:26:57,260 --> 00:26:59,560
Don't breach the natural Dao.

396
00:26:59,560 --> 00:27:01,940
Go with the flow.

397
00:27:03,439 --> 00:27:08,058
Just like the refugees in Luoyang, once they get an acre of farmland,

398
00:27:08,059 --> 00:27:10,779
they can live their life through self-reliance and build their new homes.

399
00:27:10,779 --> 00:27:16,058
They want a peaceful and steady life instead of endless killings.

400
00:27:16,059 --> 00:27:18,198
You've got a strong power of understanding.

401
00:27:18,198 --> 00:27:20,938
I want you to stay in our temple now.

402
00:27:20,939 --> 00:27:24,958
Master, where can the heavenly Dao be found?

403
00:27:24,958 --> 00:27:28,899
Nature created everything, the human is just one of them.

404
00:27:28,900 --> 00:27:31,059
You finding even your true intention,

405
00:27:31,059 --> 00:27:34,640
not to mention finding the Heavenly Dao.

406
00:27:35,860 --> 00:27:37,600
I see.

407
00:27:38,199 --> 00:27:43,779
Now, can you tell me what your true intention is?

408
00:27:43,780 --> 00:27:48,140
I thought I could recapture what I lost.

409
00:27:48,140 --> 00:27:52,580
But I didn't realize what I was withstanding until just now.

410
00:27:53,419 --> 00:27:55,660
I'm not willing to give up,

411
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:57,919
but I don't want to wait, either.

412
00:27:58,980 --> 00:28:03,899
I want to see the prosperous Great Tang in my lifetime.

413
00:28:03,899 --> 00:28:08,958
I will end the troubled times by myself and counterattack brutally.

414
00:28:08,958 --> 00:28:11,499
Are you clear about what you are saying?

415
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:13,440
Don't breach the original intention.

416
00:28:14,700 --> 00:28:18,139
Right. I misjudged.

417
00:28:18,640 --> 00:28:23,899
How could you be content with living a peaceful life?

418
00:28:51,699 --> 00:28:54,859
Madam, Sheng Xin has arranged well.

419
00:28:54,860 --> 00:28:58,859
Is Du Ruhui responsible for the security of Luoyang?

420
00:28:58,860 --> 00:28:59,818
Yes.

421
00:28:59,819 --> 00:29:01,698
But for the ceremony in White Horse Temple tomorrow,

422
00:29:01,699 --> 00:29:06,178
Du Ruhui has called up some of his people from the Ziwei Palace to the eastern suburb.

423
00:29:06,178 --> 00:29:09,178
Our people will watch their movement at all times.

424
00:29:09,179 --> 00:29:13,299
Watch out for another person for me as well.

425
00:29:14,539 --> 00:29:17,640
The one who destroyed Liang of Xiao,

426
00:29:18,339 --> 00:29:20,019
Li Jing.

427
00:29:21,740 --> 00:29:24,618
<i>Have a look here!</i>

428
00:29:24,618 --> 00:29:26,679
<i>Baubles.</i>

429
00:29:26,679 --> 00:29:28,400
<i>Come and have a look!</i>

430
00:29:29,059 --> 00:29:31,399
<i>Attention please.</i>

431
00:29:47,380 --> 00:29:49,659
Wait, wait.

432
00:29:49,660 --> 00:29:56,260
I think you should select this move called "relieving a state by besieging the other" to win.

433
00:29:57,410 --> 00:30:02,160
Do you know "a real master won't speak when seeing the game"?
<i>[Li Jing]</i>

434
00:30:02,939 --> 00:30:05,358
I helped you with kindness win a game doomed to lose,

435
00:30:05,358 --> 00:30:06,818
but you don't accept it.

436
00:30:06,819 --> 00:30:07,929
Come on.

437
00:30:07,930 --> 00:30:10,220
<i>Just play by himself if he's capable.</i>

438
00:30:16,199 --> 00:30:18,559
Where is this chilly wind from?

439
00:30:20,599 --> 00:30:22,040
Honey?

440
00:30:22,040 --> 00:30:25,358
Honey, why are you here?

441
00:30:25,358 --> 00:30:27,338
Darling, you worked so hard.

442
00:30:27,339 --> 00:30:29,019
An important guest came to visit us

443
00:30:29,020 --> 00:30:31,139
while you have no time to receive him.

444
00:30:31,140 --> 00:30:33,199
You were playing a chess game here.

445
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:35,518
What a fun day for you!

446
00:30:35,518 --> 00:30:41,139
I'm just afraid that you may be tired so I'm here to have a look.

447
00:30:41,140 --> 00:30:42,739
No, I'm not tired.

448
00:30:42,740 --> 00:30:44,340
I'm not.

449
00:30:45,140 --> 00:30:46,859
Yes, right.

450
00:30:46,860 --> 00:30:48,409
I'm very tired.

451
00:30:48,410 --> 00:30:50,438
I will go back home with you right now.

452
00:30:50,438 --> 00:30:52,120
Please, my honey.

453
00:30:54,140 --> 00:30:58,619
Honey, is the important guest at our home that person again?

454
00:30:59,299 --> 00:31:01,099
Duke Du came to our home again.

455
00:31:01,100 --> 00:31:04,138
He wanted you to take over the Ministry of War for him.

456
00:31:04,138 --> 00:31:06,139
I have refused for you.

457
00:31:07,359 --> 00:31:11,919
Having a considerate wife like you is my best luck.

458
00:31:13,780 --> 00:31:15,599
Got it.

459
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:18,578
I'll wash my hands, burn the incense, and kneel down tamely.

460
00:31:18,579 --> 00:31:20,220
Practice on my knees.

461
00:31:22,740 --> 00:31:23,718
<i>You know what?</i>

462
00:31:23,718 --> 00:31:26,779
<i>Because the crown prince is immoral, Luoyang will suffer from heavy fire.</i>

463
00:31:26,780 --> 00:31:28,238
<i>Really?</i>

464
00:31:28,238 --> 00:31:29,899
<i>Absolutely.</i>

465
00:31:29,900 --> 00:31:33,779
<i>- Think about it, who brought us the current bitter life?
- Right.</i>

466
00:31:33,779 --> 00:31:34,659
<i>- Yes.
- That's right.</i>

467
00:31:34,660 --> 00:31:35,279
<i>That's right.</i>

468
00:31:35,280 --> 00:31:37,019
<i>- It's the crown prince's misconduct.
- That's right.</i>

469
00:31:37,020 --> 00:31:38,659
<i>Or else, we wouldn't be like this.</i>

470
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:39,819
<i>- Right.
- Can't agree more.</i>

471
00:31:39,819 --> 00:31:42,578
<i>Nowadays, even Heaven can't bear him.</i>

472
00:31:42,579 --> 00:31:44,299
<i>He will receive his consequences!</i>

473
00:31:44,299 --> 00:31:46,019
<i>Perfect!</i>

474
00:31:46,020 --> 00:31:47,638
<i>- Great!
- Nice.</i>

475
00:31:47,638 --> 00:31:50,260
<i>Good, so nice!</i>

476
00:31:54,970 --> 00:31:56,609
Don't miss dinner,

477
00:31:56,610 --> 00:31:58,729
or you have to be on your knees for two hours more.

478
00:31:58,730 --> 00:32:00,130
Okay.

479
00:32:57,249 --> 00:32:59,068
Don't move.

480
00:32:59,068 --> 00:33:00,749
Who are you?

481
00:33:01,769 --> 00:33:03,329
You brat.

482
00:33:03,330 --> 00:33:05,488
How dare you spread flour at me?

483
00:33:05,489 --> 00:33:06,879
I'm warning you.

484
00:33:06,880 --> 00:33:08,049
You'd better be honest.

485
00:33:08,050 --> 00:33:10,049
Or you will be killed here, I'm serious.

486
00:33:10,050 --> 00:33:11,279
Who on earth are you?

487
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:12,989
You tailed after me and want me to speak by myself?

488
00:33:12,990 --> 00:33:14,159
What should I say?

489
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:16,820
- Who asked you to spread the rumor?
- Where is that person?

490
00:33:21,510 --> 00:33:24,010
You know who spread the rumor?

491
00:33:24,649 --> 00:33:26,570
Who are you?

492
00:33:44,450 --> 00:33:46,808
Tell us the truth. Where is she?

493
00:33:59,690 --> 00:34:01,450
He is a man of sacrifice.

494
00:34:02,129 --> 00:34:03,909
It's not her arrangement.

495
00:34:04,690 --> 00:34:06,190
Wait!

496
00:34:07,529 --> 00:34:09,029
Who is it?

497
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:14,430
<i>[Li Residence]</i>

498
00:34:38,170 --> 00:34:41,830
You often visit our home during mealtime, don't you?

499
00:34:42,370 --> 00:34:46,030
What a pity, my husband is not at home again.

500
00:34:51,289 --> 00:34:55,388
Duke Du, my husband has said many times

501
00:34:55,388 --> 00:34:57,769
that he has no intention to go to Chang'an.

502
00:34:58,429 --> 00:35:00,348
Sorry to bother you, Madam Li.

503
00:35:00,348 --> 00:35:05,788
But I still hope to have a talk with Young Master Li before I give up.

504
00:35:05,788 --> 00:35:08,229
It's up to you.

505
00:35:08,229 --> 00:35:09,970
Please enjoy it.

506
00:35:24,449 --> 00:35:26,809
He missed dinner again.

507
00:35:26,810 --> 00:35:30,089
What's worse, he left me to deal with those boring men.

