581
00:40:37,890 --> 00:40:39,548
Well... I don't know.

582
00:40:39,548 --> 00:40:41,488
Get into the palace and save the people there.

583
00:40:41,489 --> 00:40:43,289
- Hurry.
- Yes.

584
00:40:46,410 --> 00:40:49,009
Go.

585
00:40:52,130 --> 00:40:53,708
