- Go and save the people.

586
00:40:53,708 --> 00:40:55,089
You are not allowed to go there.

587
00:40:55,090 --> 00:40:57,099
The more people, the more we can do.

588
00:40:57,099 --> 00:40:58,908
You want to look for your old friend?

589
00:40:58,908 --> 00:41:01,550
